description: Meghan Markle said she experienced "cruel" online bullying while she was pregnant with both of her children.
title: Meghan Markle recounts 'cruel' online bullying during her pregnancies; is keeping distance on social media

description: ABUJA, Nigeria — Armed men broke into a boarding school in northwestern Nigeria early Saturday and seized 15 children as they slept, police told The Associated Press, about 48 hours after nearly 300 students were taken hostage in the conflict-hit region.
title: Gunmen kidnap 15 children in yet another school abduction in northern Nigeria

description: When Brittany Mahomes recently advised moms to take care of their pelvic floors, she raised awareness of a condition that is more common than many young women realize.
title: After Brittany Mahomes' advice, doctors offer ways to take care of pelvic floor problems

description: A 29-year-old woman had both of her feet amputated after she was allegedly pushed onto subway tracks in Manhattan and struck by a train following an argument with her boyfriend.
title: Woman’s feet amputated after boyfriend allegedly shoves her in front of NYC train

description: A Florida mother who was reported missing by a concerned co-worker was found alive in a shipping container after someone heard her banging on the locked door, police said.
title: Florida mother missing for days found alive in shipping container, banging on locked door

description: A "vibrant" 96-year-old widow preparing to bake cookies for her birthday was killed at her Montecito, California, home in an alleged murder-for-hire plot, according to authorities who said the case involved a "tangled evil web of financial exploitation."
title: Widow, 96, preparing to celebrate her birthday was killed in alleged murder-for-hire plot at her home

description: BENNINGTON, Vt. — A Vermont man on Friday pleaded guilty to a reduced charge of negligent driving with death resulting in the June crash that killed actor Treat Williams.
title: Driver pleads guilty to reduced charge in Vermont crash that killed actor Treat Williams

description: SAN FRANCISCO — A United Airlines jetliner headed to Mexico City from San Francisco made an emergency landing in Los Angeles on Friday after the crew reported a hydraulics issue, in the fourth emergency involving a United Airlines flight this week.
title: Mexico-bound plane lands in LA in 4th emergency this week for United Airlines

description: Born Bayard Taylor Rustin in Pennsylvania in 1912, the civil rights icon was named after Bayard Taylor, who some credit with having written America's first gay novel.
title: Bayard Rustin’s connection to queer history may have started with his very name

description: Spring breakers flocking to TX beaches this month could stumble upon a sight many have never seen — a bright blue and silver sea slug known as the blue dragon.
title: Blue dragon season is upon us, but researchers remind beachgoers to think twice before touching them

description: It may seem like mishaps involving airlines like Boeing have become more frequent, but experts say flying has rarely been safer.
title: Aviation incidents seem to be proliferating, but experts say there's no reason for alarm

description: Anti-DEI laws are wiping out tools to help Hispanic students enroll and graduate. “The elephant in the room is racism,” the president of the Hispanic Association of Colleges and Universities said.
title: Bans on diversity, equity and inclusion may halt Latino progress in higher education

description: The 60-second spot is the first in a six-week, $30 million ad buy announced by the campaign this week.
title: Biden campaign releases new ad that touches on president's age

description: Tucked away in the red-brick community center of the South Jamaica Houses in New York City is a small multipurpose room filled with plastic chairs and tables.
title: This group brings free coding education to low-income NYC students

description: The passage of an Alabama bill that aims to protect in vitro fertilization should have been a win for advocates of the fertility procedure, but it has left some legal experts around the country concerned that the new law will do more harm than good.
title: Law protecting Alabama IVF may do more harm than good, critics say

description: Two U.S. National Guard members and a Border Patrol agent were killed and a fourth person was injured when a helicopter went down near Rio Grande City, Texas, on Friday, officials said.
title: 2 soldiers, Border Patrol agent dead in helicopter crash near Texas-Mexico border

description: Nine people are dead after a van was struck by a tractor-trailer in an intersection on a Wisconsin state highway Friday, officials said.
title: 9 dead in Wisconsin crash between semi and van

description: Two roommates of a recently deceased man were each charged with abusing a corpse after propping up his body to withdraw money from his bank, police said.
title: Dead Ohio man's roommates drove body to withdraw money from his bank account, police say

description: Attorneys for Hunter Biden had urged a judge to dismiss the nine tax-related charges against him, arguing political pressure played a role in his prosecution.
title: Prosecutors say Hunter Biden invented 'a conspiracy theory' in effort to dismiss tax charges

description: Abbott has recently upped his national profile amid speculation that he’s angling to be Trump’s running mate, or perhaps his attorney general if he wins in November.
title: Texas Gov. Greg Abbott embraces role as top Biden antagonist on border

description: The largest wildfire in Texas state history was caused by a power line after a pole that “appeared to be decayed at the base” fell into a grassy area, a Texas A&M Forest Service investigator concluded in a report released Friday.
title: Broken power pole and downed wires caused largest fire in Texas history

description: President Joe Biden kicked off a travel blitz Friday after his State of the Union address, heading to the critical swing state of Pennsylvania to drive home some of the key points he delivered during Thursday's address.
title: Biden kicks off post-State of the Union travel blitz in Pennsylvania

description: While some Democrats said they were unhappy with Biden's use of "an illegal" in his State of the Union speech, they said the benefits of his policies shouldn't be ignored.
title: 'Disappointing': Biden's reference to 'an illegal' upsets some Democratic allies

description: Over 100 children have died of the flu this season, the CDC reported Friday. Experts say vaccines are a key source of prevention.
title: More than 100 kids have died of flu this year. Many were previously healthy.
